template: SELECT MIN(aka_title.kind_id) AS aka_title_kind_id FROM company_type, movie_info, aka_title, title, movie_link, kind_type, movie_keyword, company_name, cast_info, info_type, link_type, movie_companies, char_name, person_info WHERE aka_title.movie_id = title.id AND kind_type.id = aka_title.kind_id AND cast_info.movie_id = title.id AND cast_info.person_role_id = char_name.id AND company_name.id = movie_companies.company_id AND company_type.id = movie_companies.company_type_id AND info_type.id = movie_info.info_type_id AND info_type.id = person_info.info_type_id AND kind_type.id = title.kind_id AND link_type.id = movie_link.link_type_id AND movie_companies.movie_id = title.id AND movie_info.movie_id = title.id AND movie_keyword.movie_id = title.id AND movie_link.movie_id = title.id AND company_type.kind = %s AND kind_type.kind IN ('movie', 'episode', 'series') AND movie_companies.note LIKE %s AND title.production_year < %s AND title.episode_nr < %s AND title.production_year BETWEEN 1955 AND 2000 AND person_info.note = %s AND company_name.country_code != %s AND movie_info.info IN ('Drama', 'Horror', 'Thriller', 'Action', 'Sci-Fi') AND title.episode_nr > %s AND company_name.name NOT LIKE %s AND movie_companies.note NOT LIKE %s AND movie_info.note LIKE %s AND company_name.country_code = %s AND link_type.link LIKE %s AND info_type.info = %s;
